token_info.name: Seeds of Numbers (album preview)
token_info.description: Seeds of Numbers is an A/V album by visual artist Luca Scarlatta (@lo.sti.nspa.ce) and musician Emanuele Balia (@lcc01234art) powered by Umanesimo Artificiale (@umanesimo.artificiale). The work is a research into synthetical representation of a flower. The music is generated through a custom-made software on MaxMSP.
